data.description: If you are looking for a specific property which has four bedrooms, two baths, on an acreage close to both Mount Ayr and Diagonal - close enough to run home between school activities - don't pass on this opportunity!!  This larger ranch-style (over 2300 sq. ft) has an open kitchen with peninsula inviting living room guests to snack at the bar while the cook prepares all the goodies.  On the opposite end, the bonus great room (30 x 15) is that extra space your guests will be drawn into for the large screen media productions and sporting events.  The master bedroom suite has large double closets and bathroom complete with double vanity, garden tub, stand alone shower and bidet.  Surrounded by Ringgold County's lush fields, you are sure to enjoy wildlife in your backyard and serenity galore!!
